Package io.proximax.upload

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractByteStreamParameterData
    This model class is one type of the upload parameter data that defines a byte stream upload
    ByteArrayParameterData
    This model class is one type of the upload parameter data that defines a byte array upload
    FileParameterData
    This model class is one type of the upload parameter data that defines a file upload
    FilesAsZipParameterData
    This model class is one type of the upload parameter data that defines a zip upload
    InputStreamParameterData
    This model class is one type of the upload parameter data that defines a file upload
    PathParameterData
    This model class is one type of the upload parameter data that defines a path upload
    StringParameterData
    This model class is one type of the upload parameter data that defines a string upload
    Uploader
    The Uploader class that handles the upload functionality

    The Uploader creation requires a ConnectionConfig that defines generally where and how the upload will be done.
    UploadParameter
    This model class is the input parameter of upload.
    UploadParameterBuilder
    This builder class creates the UploadParameter
    UploadParameterData
    The abstract model class that defines the common fields of an upload data
    UploadResult
    The model class that defines the result of an upload.
    UrlResourceParameterData
    This model class is one type of the upload parameter data that defines a URL resource upload
